                name_value.input(name)

            individual_resume_save_btn.tap()

            time.sleep(3)

            """业务介绍"""
            business_introduction_btn_list = self.page.get_elements(home_create_other_manual_business_introduction_element,max_timeout=max_timeout)

            for business_introduction_btn in business_introduction_btn_list:
                if business_introduction_btn.text == home_create_other_manual_business_introduction_name:
                    business_introduction_btn.tap()

            time.sleep(3)

            # 输入 文字
            # 随机生成1-30字 文字
            self.logger.info("生成随机文本内容...")
            random_name = random_text_generator.generate_random_text(
                min_len=1,
                max_len=300,
                chinese_ratio=0.8  # 80%中文+20%英文
            )
            self.logger.info(f"生成随机文本（长度：{len(random_name)} 字）：{random_name}")

            # 检查必填项 文字输入框
            business_introduction_textarea_value = self.page.get_element(home_create_other_manual_business_introduction_textarea_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)
            if business_introduction_textarea_value.value == "":
                business_introduction_textarea_value.input(random_name)

                # 验证输入内容是否正确
                inputted_text = business_introduction_textarea_value.attribute("value")
                assert inputted_text == [random_name], f"输入内容不一致：预期{[random_name]}，实际{inputted_text}"
                self.logger.info(f"添加文字成功：{inputted_text} ")

            business_introduction_text = self.page.get_element(home_create_other_manual_business_introduction_text_tag,inner_text=home_create_other_manual_business_introduction_text_name,max_timeout=max_timeout)
            business_introduction_text.tap()

            # 上传 图片
            # 随机上传 1 张图片
            choose_count = 1

            # 1. 获取mock图片数据（选3张，传None则随机1-9张）
            mock_items = get_mock_image_items(choose_count=choose_count)

            # 2. 核心：调用minium原生mock方法（自动拦截chooseImage/chooseMedia/takePhoto）
            self.app.mock_choose_images(items=mock_items)

            image_btn = self.page.get_element(selector=home_create_other_manual_business_introduction_image_tag, inner_text=home_create_other_manual_business_introduction_image_name,
                                              max_timeout=max_timeout)
            image_btn.tap()

            # 避免等待时间不足，上传失败
            sleep = 5 * choose_count
            time.sleep(sleep)

            # # 上传 视频
            # # 随机上传 1 个视频
            # choose_count = 1
            #
            # # 1. 获取mock图片数据（选3张，传None则随机1-9张）
            # mock_items = get_mock_video_items(choose_count=choose_count)
            #
            # # 2. 核心：调用minium原生mock方法（自动拦截chooseImage/chooseMedia/takePhoto）
            # self.app.mock_choose_images(items=mock_items)
            #
            # image_btn = self.page.get_element(selector=home_create_other_manual_business_introduction_video_tag, inner_text=home_create_other_manual_business_introduction_video_name,
            #                                   max_timeout=max_timeout)
            # image_btn.tap()
            #
            # time.sleep(20)

            # 点击保存
            individual_resume_save_btn = self.page.get_element(home_create_other_manual_individual_resume_save_element,max_timeout=max_timeout)
            individual_resume_save_btn.tap()

            time.sleep(3)

            create_btn = self.page.get_element(home_create_other_manual_btn_element,max_timeout=max_timeout)
            create_btn.tap()

            for i in range(10):
                if self.app.current_page != find_create_other_detail_page_url:
                    time.sleep(1)

            if self.app.current_page == find_create_other_detail_page_url:
                self.logger.info(f"文字转名片创建个人说明书成功_用户名：{name} _手机号：{phone}")
                timestamp = time.strftime("%H%M%S")
                self.capture(f"文字转名片创建个人说明书成功_用户名：{name} _手机号：{phone}_{timestamp}.png")
            else:
                timestamp = time.strftime("%H%M%S")
                self.capture(f"文字转名片创建个人说明书失败，请手动检查_{timestamp}.png")
                assert self.app.current_page == find_create_other_detail_page_url, f"文字转名片创建个人说明书失败，请手动检查"

        except Exception as e:
            self.logger.error(f"文字转名片创建个人说明书失败：{str(e)}")
            # 异常时截图
            timestamp = time.strftime("%H%M%S")
            self.capture(f"文字转名片创建个人说明书失败，请手动检查_{timestamp}.png")
            raise

        time.sleep(2)
